  <brief_title>Randomized Study In Severe Aplastic Anemia Patients Receiving Atg, Cyclosporin A, With Or Without G-CSF (SAA-G-CSF)</brief_title>
  <acronym>SAA-G-CSF</acronym>
  <official_title>A RANDOMIZED CONTROLLED STUDY IN NEWLY DIAGNOSED SEVERE APLASTIC ANEMIA PATIENTS RECEIVING ANTITHYMOCYTE GLOBULIN (ATG), CYCLOSPORIN A, WITH OR WITHOUT G-CSF</official_title>
